Name: Event
Description: Base type for all events in the system

Name: Parameter
Description: Information about individual parameters within data products

Name: ParameterCharacteristicsReport
Description: Information about accuracy, drift, precision, etc.

Name: CodeReport
Description: gives explanation of each code used in a coded parameter, such as the meaning of QC flags

Name: GeospatialCoordinateReferenceSystem
Description: Hold information about the geospatial coordinate reference system(s) used

Name: DeviceMountingPosition
Description: Provides information specific to the mounting of an instrument on a platform

Name: TemporalBounds
Description: Defines a time bounds through a start and end datetime pair

Name: UserSubscription
Description: Information on users who have subscribed to acquire data (does not apply to processes that "subscribe" to streams)

Name: Term
Description: This object allows the association of an authority with a term

Name: ExternalArchive
Description: Holds information on where and when a data product was submitted to an external archive
